# bgremove

Local background removal built on [`rembg`](https://github.com/danielgatis/rembg).
Includes a Python CLI and a FastAPI server.

## Quick start (macOS / Apple Silicon)

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url> rembg-tool && cd rembg-tool
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
make dev
